@_Rian_Stone @redpilldadpua @AusDaygame @DexterDaygame While true, it gets weird when everybody's lyin'.

The technical lit I got with the shots plus a lil' extra research to fill the gaps backed up my gut instinct of "a vaccine can't be worse than the virus".

Beyond that, I've never known a gov't to not fuck up it's own conspiracy.

@_Rian_Stone @redpilldadpua @AusDaygame @DexterDaygame The former, I presume.

It's such a weird stance to me, how do people be more scared of a vaccine than the actual disease?

My only criticism of mRNA is stealth rolling it out as a normal vaccine makes anti-vax look more valid than it is.
